de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.tnccs.im.loader.simple

Class DefaultImLoader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.tnccs.im.loader.simple.DefaultImLoader<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the loadable type (e.g. IMC or IMV)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImLoader<T>

    public class DefaultImLoader<T>
extends Object
implements ImLoader<T>
    Default loader to load IM(C/V) according to a configuration entry. It handles the class path for the loaded IM(C/V) by managing a set of URL class loaders.
